  “Siong2-sian7 hoat8-ok” che-si7 thian-hoat; sui-jian5 u7 lang5 kong2, “Sian7-sim e5 to2 teh go7, ok-sim e5 ti3 se-bo7,” “cho3-ok cho3 tok8 khia5 be2 khok8-khok8,” u7 khah bo5 siu-iong2 e5 soa3 kong2, “ThiN-li2 bo5 bak8,” goa2 kong2 li2 m7-thang hiah toa7 chhui3-tau2, tui3 thiN hiah bo5 le2. “Thian-li2 chiau-chiau, si5-sin5 be7 to3 m7-si7 ho2 phaiN2 bo5 po3,” in-ui7 po3-eng3 u7 kin2 ban7 e5 cheng-chha. An2-ni khoaN3 choe7-ok tek-khak u7 kang-chiN5(po3-eng3). Kang-chiN5 si7 sim2-mih8? Si7 khoaN3 li2 e5 in lai5 kiat-ko2. Siok8-gu2 kong2, “Cheng3 tau7 siu tau7, cheng3 chhek siu chhek.” Ho5-se-a 8: 7 kong2, Sou2 cheng3 e5 si7 hong, sou2 siu e5 si7 kng2-le5-hong.” Lo5-ma2 6:23 kong2, “Choe7-ok e5 kang-chiN5 si7 si2, chit e5 si2 si7 choe3 thang kiaN e5 heng5-hoat88.” An2-ni thang siuN7. 
  Choe3 phaiN2 e5 lang5 m7-thang khoa-khau2, kong2 ham3-ham3 lah! ChhiuN2 iaN5 si7 siau3. Chu2 tek-khak e7 lai5 kap li2 chheng-sng3. U7 chit8-tui3 chheng-lian5 hu-hu7, ka-teng5 chin oan5-boan2, saN-thiaN3 teh koe3-jit8, au7-lai5 tiong7-hu tioh8 ai3 chhut-goa7, chiu7 ka7 I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2, li2 ai3 kin2-siu2 ka-hong, keng3 toa7 thiaN3 se3, hu7-jin5-lang5 in3 kong2, “Cho3 li2 an-sim.” Tiong7-hu ia7 thok I chit8 e5 chi3 chhin-bit8 e5 peng5-iu2 kong2, ti7 I chhut-goa7 tiong ka7 I koan-sim I e5 ka-teng5. Hu7-jin5-lang5 chui2-seng3 khah nng2-chiaN2, bo5 ku2 siu7 in2-iu2 te3 tioh8 chit8 e5 siau3-lian5 lang5, chit e5 siu7-thok e5 peng5-iu2 chai, teh siuN7 pat8-jit8 beh an2-choaN2 po3-ko3 chit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 sou2 kiaN5, I chiu7 chiong chit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap hit e5 siau3-lian5 sou2 kiaN5 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7 it-it ka7 thau hip siong7 kap liok8-im khi2-lai5. Peng5-iu2 to3-lai5 lah, I chiu7 chiong I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 su7 po3-ko3, soa3 chiong sou2 hip e5 siong7 kap sou2 liok8 e5 im hou7 I khoaN3. Tiong7-hu mng7 I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, hu7-jin5-lang5 lau2-a2 ke2 seng3-jin5, teh siuN7 I e5 su7 chin ki5-bit8, ke-lai7 bo5 lang5 chai, sin5-kui2 ia7 m7-chai, chiu7 teh se2 chheng, au7-lai5 I e5 tiong7-hu chiong I e5 peng5-iu2 sou2 hip e5 oah8-tang7 sia2-chin ka7 cho3 chhut-lai5, hu7-jin5-lang5 khoaN3 chit8 kiN3, khui-siaN toa7-khau3, jin7-choe7. Bat lang5 sim-lai7 e5 Siong7-te3, I m7-bian2 lang5 ka7 I kong2. Siong7-te3 khoan-iong5 si7 beh chhoa7 li2 hoan2-hoe2, li2 na7 m7 hoan2-hoe2, koh beh chiu2-chui3 hong3-tong7, oan-ke saN-phah, Chu2 kau3, khoaN3 li2 an2-ni kiaN5, beh tang7-tang7 heng5-hoat8 li2...(Ma2-thai3 24:49, 51). 
  KhoaN3-tioh8 phaiN2-lang5 teh heng-ong7, m7-thang put-peng5. 
  Tioh8 chai “Thian-bong2 khoe-khoe sou ji5 put-lou7.” U7 nng7-lang5 cho3-hoe2 kng-kio7, u7 chit8-jit8 kng tioh8 chit8 e5 ho2-giah8 lang5, toa3 chin-che7 gin5. Kah-a2 chio It-a2 lai5 bou5-chai5 hai7-beng7, It-a2 m7, kau3 bo5 lang5 sou2 kau3 e5 chhim-soaN, Kah-a2 chiu7 phah-si2 hu3-ong, chhiuN2 hiah e5 gin5, beh pun It-a2, It-a2 m7-tih8; Kah-a2 kiaN It-a2 ka7 lau7-siat, chiu7 eng7 I e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 hou7 It-a2 cho3 sim-pu7, hoan-hu3 I tioh8 iu2-hau3, I e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 ko2-jian5 chin iu2-hau3, saN tng3 chiah8 png7 e5 si5, long2 su-hau7 ka7 in ta-koaN te2 png7, beh ka7 te2 e5 si5, in ta-koaN tak8 pai2 to kong2, “Bo5 thiN”; kau3 u7 chit8-jit8, Kah-a2 in kiaN2 tiong3 chiong7-goan5 beh chiuN7 kiaN-siaN5 cho3 toa7 koaN, kui ke-hoe2 long2 che7 chun5, kau3 poaN3 hai2 tim5-chun5, Kah-a2 kui-ke long2 biat8-bo5, chit e5 siau-sit jip8 It-a2 e5 hi7-khang; hit e5-hng, in sim-pu7 beh koh ka7 te2 png7 e5 si5 chiu7 kong2, “U7 thiN”; in sim-pu7 chin ki5-koai3, chiah mng7, a-tia I2-cheng5 long2 kong2 bo5 thiN, kin-a2-jit8 goa2 e5 pe7-bo2, hiaN-ti7 choan5-ke biat8-bo5, li2 soa3 kong2 u7 thiN, si7 sim2-mih8 I3-su3? In ta-koaN chiong in lau7-pe7, bou5-chai5 hai7-beng7 teh heng-ong7, goa2 kio3 si7 bo5 thiN leh, taN u7 thiN lah, u7 po3-eng3 lah. (Chit nng7 lang5 chiu7-si7 Ou-ku kap Phou2-hin. (Ku7-lek8 12 goeh8 chhe 3 Ou-ku seN). 
  Liat8-ui7 ah, lan2 m7-thang kau3 khoaN3-tioh8 phaiN2-lang5 siu7 po3-eng3, chiah sin3 u7 thian-li2; Chu2 tek-khak beh lai5 sim2-phoaN3, ho2-phaiN2 tek-khak e7 hun-beng5. 
  Lan2 ai3 chai choe7-ok e5 li7-hai7. 
  “Sat-tan3 ia7 ka-ki7 chng-cho3 kng-beng5 e5 thiN-sai3” (Lim5 11:14), hou7 li2 ou-iaN2-taN7, soa3 liah8 choe7-ok cho3 sim-sek, chhin-chhiuN7 ti-tu eng7 hit ho7 thng5-bit8 tiN e5 oe7 lai5 in2-iu2 hou5-sin5. 
  Chiu2 lai5 kong2, sio2 im2 pou2 jin5 sin, chiah8 tam7-poh8 khah be7 sian7, tai7-seng lang5 chiah8 chiu2, au7-lai5 chiu2 chiah8 lang5, chiu2-chui3 gou7 kang-san. Kiau2 lai5 kong2, gu5-lok8-tai7, tai7-seng si7 sim-sek, au7-lai5 poah8 kau3 sim kong5 hoe2-jiat8, khang-khoe3 be7 kou3-tit cho3, png7 be7 kou3-tit chiah8, phah hai7 sin-the2, san3-hiong cho3 chhat8. U7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2 bin7-bou5 chin sui2, kho2-sioh tioh8 kau5, san2-san2 na2 kau5, put-si5 haiN, io kau3 khi3-sim lou2-mia7, soa3 siuN7-khi3 kong2 beh si2 ia7 m7 kin2 si2, toa3 teh leng5-ti7 lang5. Liat8-ui7 ah, m7-si7 gin2-na2 leng5-ti7 li2, si7 li2 leng5-ti7 I, I thai3-e7 m7-chiaN5 gin2-na2, si7-toa7-lang5 tui3 choe7-ok sou2 nia2 e5 moe5-tok8 kang-chiN5 lai5 lian5-lui7 li2 e5 kiaN2; sou2-I2 tioh8 me7 li2 ka-ki7. Li7-hai7 ah, choe7-ok e5 kang-chiN5, chit e5 sui2-sui2 ka-teng5, oan5-boan2 hu-hu7, choe7-ok chit8 e7 jip8-khi3, chiu7 long7-ke soaN3-theh8, li7-ian5 pun kiaN2. TaN u7 sim2-mih8 kiu3 hoat? U7. Chu2 Ia5-sou kong2, “KiN3-na7 tioh8-boa5 taN tang7-taN3 e5, tioh8 lai5 chiu7 Goa2, Goa2 beh hou7 lin2 an-hioh” (Thai3 11:28). Koh kong2, kiN3-na7 hoan7-choe7 e5, chiu7-si7 cho3 choe7 e5 lou5-chai5, KiaN2 (Ia5-sou) na7 hou7 lin2 chu7-iu5 chiu7 chin-chiaN3 chu7-iu5 (Han7 8:34, 36). Seng3-si 115 siu2, “KiN3-na7 u7 lang5 hou7 choe7 khou2-chhou2, tioh8 chhoe7 Kiu3-chu2 Ia5-sou, I e7 kiu3 li2, I beh kiu3 li2, chek-si5 chin2-kiu3 li2.” Hun3-heng koa 78. “Eng5-kng e5 thau2-pang3, ki5-biau7 e5 thau2-pang3...” Li2 ka-ki7 beh li7-khui choe7-ok si7 bo5 pan7-hoat, tioh8 kho3 Chu2 e5 po2-huih, ka7 li2 siok8-hoe5. Chhin-chhiuN7 Jit8-pun2 teh khou2-chhou2, Tai5-oan5 ka-ki7 be7 e7 thoat-li7, Beng5-kun eng7 goan5-chu2-tan5 phah kau3 hou7 Jit8-pun2 tau5-hang5, Tai5-oan5 chiu7 tit-tioh8 thau2-pang3. Chu2 e5 sip8-ji7-ke3 pi2 goan5-chu2-tan5 ke u7 chheng ban7 poe7 e5 leng5-lek8, e7 taN2-to2 Mou5-kui2, hui2-biat8 choe7-ok, hou7 lan2 bo5 koh u7 choe7-ok pe2-pak8 thong3-khou2, lai5 tiam3 ti7 in-tian2 lai7, cho3 Siong7-te3 chu7-iu5 kiaN2-ji5.
  (Tai5-oan5 Kau3-hoe7 Kong-po3 te7 788 ki5, 1954 ni5 8 goeh8)
